\id 3JN Reconstructed from Ventura Publisher
\h 3 Zon
\toc1 Khe Zon Gava Phuni Khergiap, Ana Wom Khergi Khegene Khare
\toc2 3 Zon
\toc3 3 Zo
\mt1 3 ZON
\mt2 Khe Zon Gava Phuni Khergiap, Ana Wom Khergi Khegene Khare.
\imt1 Khe fharav gan…®nga buni khare.
\ip Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi gari guman pana mbe kha gava khergiap, harigi guman pana mbe ndi mbai. Mba guman pana z…® khare, Gaius. Ana Gaius z…® ndi vun kuamkuagi. Ana khaŇč muuŇčgi ne nzuav, ana guigira Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigir, ana mben kurkurigi. Ana Gaius z…® ndi vun kuamkuav vh…®ra, ana gori ruav khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu kha guman r…®v…®ri. Mba guma z…® khare Diotrefes.‚ÄĚ
\c 1
\ms1 Nza Fhe Bak…®men Ňčaara mbui gumgi, nza mben kurkurarga.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt FG 19.29; Ro 16.23; 1 Ko 1.14; 2 Zo 1.1\x*Gu Zisas Krais khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi gari guman pan, gu kha gava khergiap, ndu Gaius, gu anan ndu ndi mbai. Ndu nan k…®vntoga guar ma. Gu guigira won ndavar ndu n…®…®Ňčgi.
\p 
\v 2 Ndu nan k…®vntoga vhuuŇč ma, gu ndu nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai, ndu mbui bigi, nta h…®r…® t…®var vhuun muunga, ndu vh…®ra nzerara k…®rga. Gu kaŇčgi, ndun vhen ki guma, ana nzerara ki.
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt 2 Zo 1.4\x*Fhum Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi mbari, mbe zav, na garav, khaŇč na suaŇčgi, ndu guigira buna guareŇč z…®n vui guma ma. Gu mba kameŇč mbararagiap, gu guigira ndikndigi. Gu kaŇčgi, ndu zazera buna guareŇčra z…®n vui.
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt 1 Ko 4.15; Fm 1.10\x*Gu kav, mbararagi, nan tari buna guareŇč z…®n vui, gu guigira ndikndigi. Gu nen ndikndigi ndikndik, ana guigira gu mba harigi bigi ga nzuav ndikndigi ndikndik kambarigi.
\s1 Gaius Ňčaara vhuuŇčra mbui.
\p 
\v 5 Ndu nan k…®vntoga vhuuŇč, ndu buni guari, ndu zaaŇčtuigira nta z…®n vuav, ndu t…®var vhuuŇčra Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, ndu kurkurar vhuun mbe mbui. Ndu maaŇč mbe mbuav, ndu vh…®ra, kakagi gumgi, ndu vh…®ra t…®var vhuun mbe mbui.
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Ta 3.13\x*Mba guigira Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi, ndu mba t…®vara vhuuaŇč mbe muuŇčgim, mbe zav khaŇč Zisas khoth…®gap, ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi phorga nzuav, ndu guigira won ndavar mbe n…®…®Ňčgiap, mbe muuŇčgi t…®vi, mbe nta bun mbe suaŇčgi. Ne t…®var vhuuŇč ma. Mbe taagip mba tuavar Ňčg…®rim, ndu taagip mbe ndigi mba tuavar Ňčg…®rga bigira mben kurarim, mbe Ňčg…®ri. Ndu Fhe Bak…®me vuzvuga z…®n Ňčg…®p, ana mben kurkurargane vuzvugi bigira mben kurari.
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt 1 Ko 9.12; 9.15\x*Mbe Zisas Ňčaarar muungeŇč nd…®knd…®ga vov, mba Ňčaara mbui. Mbe mba Ňčaara mbuav, mbe Zisas khoth…®gap, ana z…®n Ňčg…® thagi gumgi, mbe mben han bigi ndi fhuvara.
\v 8 Nza mba khesharigi gumgi, nza mben kurkurarga. Nza mba t…®va mbui, nza mbe phorgap nza wari t…®gap mba Ňčaara mbuav, nza Fhe Bak…®me buna guareŇč, nza wari t…®gap ne havhari.
\s1 Diotrefes t…®va mbat…®ga mbui.
\p 
\v 9 Gu buni mbari khergiap, guigira Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi mbari ndi mbarigi. Diotrefes, ana mbe gari guma bak…®me k…®r za mbuav, ana nza nzuai buni mbararagi fhu.
\v 10 Gu maaŇč muuŇčgip, gu nde han Ňčg…®p, gu ana mbui t…®vir nde neŇčg…®rga. Ana mbark…®rga buni mbat…®gira nza nzuai. Ana mba t…®vara nza mbui fhuvara. Ana vh…®ra kha t…®va mbui, ana fegutari ndiav, wo phena vui fhu. Ana vh…®ra gari, harigi gumgi mbe ndiav, wari wo phenin Ňčg…®r za mbuim, ana mbe th…®vav, mbe vharvharav, ana vh…®ra guigira Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, ana mbe sh…®gi.
\s1 Demitrius t…®var vhuuaŇč mbui.
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Sng 37.27; Ais 1.16-17; 1 Pi 3.11; 1 Zo 3.6-10\x*Ndu nan k…®vntogar vhuuŇč, ndu t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi mbui t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…® thari. Ndu t…®vir vhuuiŇčra muuŇčri. T…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui guma, ana Fhe Bak…®me guma ma. T…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui guma, ana Fhe Bak…®me gangiap, ana kaŇčgi fhuvara.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Zo 19.35; 21.24; 1 T 3.7\x*Gumgi vh…®rve, mbe zam Demitrius mbui t…®vir vhuuiŇč bun nzuai. Mbe ana bun nzuaim, Fhe Bak…®men buni guari vh…®ra anan t…®vir vhuuiŇč bun nzuai. Nza vh…®ra anan t…®vir vhuuiŇč bun nzuai, ndu kaŇčgi, nza buni guigira.
\s1 Guman pan Gaius gan…® za mbui.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt 2 Zo 1.12\x*Gu buni vh…®rve khergiap, ndu ndi mbae, gu thagi. Gu gavar mba buni khergip, ndu ndi maaŇč thagi.
\v 14 Gu kaŇčgi, tugar mpeeŇč fhuvara. Gu nduara ndun han mbar Ňčg…®p, Ňčka wani khomani gan…®v, mba buni suanga.
\p 
\v 15 Ndu ntigem ndav mb…®rav, k…®ri. Khe ndun k…®vntogi ndu ndi mbai raar vhuuŇč khare, ‚ÄúRaar vhuuŇč‚ÄĚ. Ndu na raar vhuuŇč ndiv, maaŇč ki k…®vntogi, ndu zam mben n…®…®Ňčgiri.
